<subSubSection id="C1854D0D2077457CC042D163B6C5527F" pageId="0" pageNumber="115" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="0B88DB2F8F50B3C8FB55CC8FAD81F612" pageId="0" pageNumber="115">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="5D8749F20650D5E724B8F7D7814D9B9F" pageId="0" pageNumber="115">This species was observed only in epilithic sample from a sampling site called Fenjiezhou Island located on the coast of Hainan Island, NW South China Sea (China) in sample SZCZ27176.</paragraph>
